## The ENTIRE assets/ folder is distributed out-of-band (Google Drive), never git:
## images (png/jpg/psd), sprite atlases + their .spritemeta/.animationmeta sidecars,
## audio, and the large maps under assets/maps/. A fresh clone has an empty assets/ —
## copy it in from the shared Drive folder (see tools/sync-binaries.ps1).
## Everything git-tracked that used to live in assets/ moved OUT: UI definitions ->
## data/ui/, fonts -> resources/fonts/.
assets/

